values.description:
While trying to serialize protobuf messages, I ran into the problem that the output of `SerializeToString` and `SerializeToOstream` are not UTF-8, so that can't be put into a `string` field.

Changing the field to `bytes` solves the issue while maintaining large part of the API (i.e. `msg.set_component("banana")` is still valid), but it breaks some API and ABI, so I'm targeting this to v4.
values.title: Change serialized field from string to bytes
